Sentencas: After aging, the surface of the composite cathode and the interface between the composite cathode and the electrolyte was investigated with scanning electron microscopy (SEM).

Sentencas: The performance of the half cell SOFCs degraded after aging with/without polarization compared to the initial state.
Titulo: Durability of (Pr0.7Sr0.3)MnO3±δ/8YSZ composite cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SOFCs had a larger polarization resistance after 1000 h of aging.
Titulo: Durability of (Pr0.7Sr0.3)MnO3±δ/8YSZ composite cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cathodic current was shown to have an impact on the performance by slowing down the rate of decrease of polarization resistance of the SOFCs.
Titulo: Durability of (Pr0.7Sr0.3)MnO3±δ/8YSZ composite cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells
